<term>觀察使</term>韓滉表贊治有異行<pc>，</pc>加金紫<pc>，</pc>徙<placeName>常州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>滉輔政<pc>，</pc>分所統為<num value="3">三</num>道<pc>，</pc>以贊為<placeName>宣州</placeName>
<term>刺史</term>
<pc>、</pc>都團練<term>觀察使</term>
<pc>，</pc>治宣<measure quantity="10" unit="years">
