</div>
<div>
<p>贊曰<pc>：</pc>
<date notBefore="9999" notAfter="9999">唐</date>興<pc>，</pc>史官秉筆眾矣<pc>。</pc>然垂<measure quantity="300" unit="years">
<num value="300">三百</num>年</measure>
